@node Image-Build and Filesystem-Creation Constants
@appendixsec Image-Build and Filesystem-Creation Constants

The image-building scripts also encode important assumptions:

@multitable @columnfractions .35 .20 .45
@headitem Constant @tab Value @tab Meaning
@item Disk image size @tab @code{128 MiB} @tab Raw GPT disk size created by
@file{tools/make_gpt_disk.sh}
@item BIOS GRUB partition @tab @code{1 MiB-3 MiB} @tab Reserved boot area on
